SubjectAbegweit Band (PEI) SETTING APART
PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the ABEGWEIT BAND, of 1.78 hectares (4.4 acres) of land, excluding mines and minerals, in the County of Queens, south of the Charlottetown Harbour, Prince Edward Island, as an addition to ROCKY POINT INDIAN RESERVE No. 3.
